	DESC:You aided the Jeweled Sages in their hour of need, and they quickly answer your calls for help. Once per scenario when you're adventuring in Absalom or Osirion, a sage can offer advice on any subject, granting you a +5 insight bonus on one Knowledge skill check. You can check a box in front of this boon to instead receive direct attention from a sage anywhere. The sage attempts a trained Knowledge skill check for you, with a bonus equal to twice your character level, and provides the information to you through mental magical communication.

