	DESC:Torch has developed a grudging respect or passing fondness for you and makes an effort to avoid harming you. When interacting with Torch or his agents, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus on Bluff, Diplomacy, and Intimidate checks. If you would die while fighting Grandmaster Torch or his agents, you can cross this boon off your Chronicle sheet to return to life with 0 hit points at the end of the encounter.
